  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to libcdio</title>

    <para>The <application>libcdio</application> is a library for CD-ROM and CD
    image access. The assiciated <application>libcido-cdparanoia</application>
    library reads audio from the CD-ROM directly as data, with no analog step
    between, and writes the data to a file or pipe as .wav, .aifc or as raw 16
    bit linear PCM.  </para>

    &lfs7a_checked;

